        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "The most problem of all PDF creators is i18n. For arabic and persian languages we need two feature.\r\n* Right to left (http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Right-to-left)\r\n** \"\u0633\u0644\u0627\u0645 \u0628\u0631 \u0634\u0645\u0627 \u0627\u06cc \u062f\u0648\u0633\u062a\u0627\u0646.\" {color:red}Dot character must be the left position of sentence. This page is Left to right also in PDF.{color} \r\n* Joined characters\r\n** \"\u0633\u0644\u0627\u0645\" {color:green}correct{color} \r\n** \"\u0633\u200c\u0644\u200c\u0627\u200c\u0645\" {color:red}wrong{color} \r\n\r\nThis two may help Zend i18n more feature. Thanks.\r\nUseful : http:\/\/www.tcpdf.org\/\r\nPersian and Arabic language on RTL document in TCPDF:\r\nhttp:\/\/www.tcpdf.org\/examples\/example_018.pdf"
